#armor
type spell
priority 9
on You feel someone protecting you.
on You are already armored.
off You feel less armored.

#bless
type spell
priority 9
on You feel righteous.
off You feel less righteous.

#sanctuary
type spell
priority 1
on You are surrounded by a white aura.
on You are already in sanctuary.
off The white aura around your body fades.

#protective shield
type spell
priority 2
on You are surrounded by a protective shield.
off Your protective shield fades away.

